{"route":{"route":"/posts/59c8ffd6/","outputPath":"posts/59c8ffd6/index.html","kind":"post","title":"linux PPPOE拨号上网","language":"zh-Hans","params":{"abbrlink":"59c8ffd6"}},"description":"安装rp pppoe 配置 这里输入网络运营商提供给你的用户名. 这里输入你链接网络的网卡,可以使用ip addr进行查看 比如eth1,wlo1. 这里可以直接回车 这里输入两个DNS,比如1.1.1.1,8.8.8.8. 这里输入网络运营商提供给你的密码. 这里我使用1,可以按照自己的需求选择防火墙配置. 启用 可","post":{"kind":"post","sourcePath":"source/_posts/linux-PPPOE拨号上网.md","route":"/posts/59c8ffd6/","abbrlink":"59c8ffd6","title":"linux PPPOE拨号上网","date":"2020-02-08 16:26:57","updated":"2020-02-08 16:26:57","tags":["linux","archlinux"],"categories":["linux"],"language":"zh-Hans","htmlLang":"zh-Hans","locale":"zh_CN","textDirection":"ltr","dateLocale":"zh-CN","excerptMarkdown":"","excerptHtml":"","bodyMarkdown":"","bodyHtml":"<h2 id=\"安装rp-pppoe\">安装rp-pppoe</h2>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">pacman -S rp-pppoe</span></span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"配置\">配置</h2>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-built_in\">sudo</span> pppoe-setup</span></span></code></pre>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">&gt;&gt;&gt; Enter your PPPoE user name:</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>这里输入网络运营商提供给你的用户名.</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">&gt;&gt;&gt; Enter the Ethernet interface connected to the DSL modem</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">For Solaris, this is likely to be something like /dev/hme0.</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">For Linux, it will be ethn, <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">where</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;n&#x27;</span> is a number. :</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>这里输入你链接网络的网卡,可以使用<code>ip addr</code>进行查看 比如<code>eth1</code>,<code>wlo1</code>.</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">&gt;&gt;&gt; Enter the demand value (default no):</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>这里可以直接回车</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">&gt;&gt;&gt; Enter the DNS information here:</span></span></code></pre>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">&gt;&gt;&gt; Enter the secondary DNS server address here:</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>这里输入两个DNS,比如<code>1.1.1.1</code>,<code>8.8.8.8</code>.</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">&gt;&gt;&gt; Please enter your PPPoE password:  </span></span></code></pre>\n<p>这里输入网络运营商提供给你的密码.</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">The firewall choices are:</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">0 - NONE: This script will not <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">set</span> any firewall rules.  You are responsible</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">          <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> ensuring the security of your machine.  You are STRONGLY</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">          recommended to use some kind of firewall rules.</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">1 - STANDALONE: Appropriate <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> a basic stand-alone web-surfing workstation</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">6</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">2 - MASQUERADE: Appropriate <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> a machine acting as an Internet gateway</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">7</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">                <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> a LAN</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">8</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">&gt;&gt;&gt; Choose a <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">type</span> of firewall (0-2):</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>这里我使用1,可以按照自己的需求选择防火墙配置.</p>\n<h2 id=\"启用\">启用</h2>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-built_in\">sudo</span> pppoe-start</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>可以使用<code>ip addr</code>进行查看,现在应该有一个<code>ppp0</code>的网络.</p>\n<h2 id=\"查看路由确认启用\">查看路由确认启用</h2>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">[ ~ ] route</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">Kernel IP routing table</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">Destination     Gateway         Genmask         Flags Metric Ref    Use Iface</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">default         0.0.0.0         0.0.0.0         U     0      0        0 ppp0</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">                                ...</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">6</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">                                ...</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">7</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span></code></pre>\n<p>如果没有default到ppp0的这条路由,需要手动创建:</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-built_in\">sudo</span> route add default dev ppp0</span></span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"引用\">引用</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.cnblogs.com/viusuangio/p/7112674.html\">archlinux pppoe拨号连接使用详解[转载]</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.librehat.com/guide-on-linux-ppp-over-wireless-network/\">Linux下连接无线网络后拨号（即PPP over WiFi）</a></li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>\n","rawMarkdown":"","plainText":"","toc":[{"id":"安装rp-pppoe","text":"安装rp-pppoe","level":2},{"id":"配置","text":"配置","level":2},{"id":"启用","text":"启用","level":2},{"id":"查看路由确认启用","text":"查看路由确认启用","level":2},{"id":"引用","text":"引用","level":2}],"slugForSearch":"59c8ffd6","comments":true,"math":false,"mermaid":false}}